294
00:13:59,460 --> 00:14:01,140
I always win people over with virtue.

295
00:14:02,570 --> 00:14:05,910
♪Can't tell♪

296
00:14:08,860 --> 00:14:10,940
Is this winning people over with virtue?

297
00:14:11,820 --> 00:14:13,180
This is seduction.

298
00:14:15,100 --> 00:14:15,940
Gross.

299
00:14:17,460 --> 00:14:18,780
Should I offer myself instead?

300
00:14:19,620 --> 00:14:20,460
Really?

301
00:14:24,350 --> 00:14:27,850
♪It's becoming clear♪

302
00:14:28,420 --> 00:14:32,730
♪My overwhelming emotions♪

303
00:14:34,960 --> 00:14:37,880
