304
00:14:40,380 --> 00:14:41,220
What's going on?

305
00:14:41,220 --> 00:14:42,620
Why are you so mushy today?

306
00:14:44,260 --> 00:14:46,420
Have a business trip tomorrow.
Don't want to leave.

307
00:14:47,450 --> 00:14:50,320
♪I've got your back from now on♪

308
00:14:52,140 --> 00:14:52,980
Hop in.

309
00:14:56,830 --> 00:15:01,580
