311
00:15:07,860 --> 00:15:09,660
(Yixiu Found of Food)

312
00:15:19,660 --> 00:15:20,820
(Sheng Nina)
I'm back.

313
00:15:21,190 --> 00:15:22,050
Are you and Mr. Jiang

314
00:15:22,060 --> 00:15:23,820
free to have dinner recently?

315
00:15:23,820 --> 00:15:25,420
(Cheng Hui)

316
00:15:25,420 --> 00:15:26,260
Let me ask.

317
00:15:44,260 --> 00:15:45,100
Peng Si.

318
00:15:45,220 --> 00:15:46,500
- Mr. Cheng.
- Where's Jiang?

319
00:15:46,780 --> 00:15:47,780
He's on a business trip.

320
00:15:48,700 --> 00:15:49,540
When will he be back?

321
00:15:50,540 --> 00:15:52,140
Probably in three or four days.

322
00:15:52,140 --> 00:15:53,380
It should be next week.

323
00:15:54,540 --> 00:15:55,380
Okay.

324
00:15:55,500 --> 00:15:56,380
I'll get back to work.

325
00:15:59,580 --> 00:16:00,900
(Sheng)
He's on a business trip.

326
00:16:00,900 --> 00:16:02,100
(Cheng)
He's back next week.

327
00:16:03,300 --> 00:16:04,660
(Sheng)
I'll leave next Monday.

328
00:16:05,580 --> 00:16:07,460
Looks like the steak will have to wait.

329
00:16:16,060 --> 00:16:16,900
Director Qin.

330
00:16:17,620 --> 00:16:18,780
I need to ask you something.

331
00:16:19,260 --> 00:16:20,100
What is it?

332
00:16:20,100 --> 00:16:21,860
You've been at CBBC for a while.

333
00:16:21,860 --> 00:16:23,820
Do you know someone named Xu Shanshan?

334
00:16:24,700 --> 00:16:27,020
She used to work in loan management.

335
00:16:27,420 --> 00:16:29,580
Xu Shanshan?

336
00:16:29,740 --> 00:16:30,580
Yeah.

337
00:16:31,180 --> 00:16:33,380
I think there is such a person,

338
00:16:34,820 --> 00:16:36,100
but I don't have much impression.

339
00:16:37,060 --> 00:16:38,220
Maybe she didn't

340
00:16:38,220 --> 00:16:39,460
stay long here.

341
00:16:39,780 --> 00:16:41,260
Many people come to the bank,

342
00:16:41,260 --> 00:16:42,420
stay for two years,

343
00:16:42,420 --> 00:16:44,180
get to know everyone,

344
00:16:44,420 --> 00:16:46,460
and then jump to companies

345
00:16:46,460 --> 00:16:47,300
to work.

346
00:16:50,180 --> 00:16:51,620
Why do you need to find her?

347
00:16:52,460 --> 00:16:53,300
Nothing.

348
00:16:53,500 --> 00:16:55,180
She and I went to the same college.

349
00:16:56,180 --> 00:16:57,900
A classmate of hers wants to find her.

350
00:16:57,900 --> 00:16:59,380
Since I'm at CBBC,

351
00:16:59,620 --> 00:17:00,700
I was asked to help.

352
00:17:01,620 --> 00:17:03,740
If you really want to find her,

353
00:17:04,260 --> 00:17:06,500
I can introduce you to someone.

354
00:17:06,860 --> 00:17:08,540
She's Lin Qin from the HR department.

355
00:17:08,540 --> 00:17:09,980
She's been at CBBC for 20 years.

356
00:17:09,980 --> 00:17:11,100
She knows everyone.

357
00:17:12,500 --> 00:17:13,340
Okay.

358
00:17:13,860 --> 00:17:15,780
Please introduce me to her.

359
00:17:16,260 --> 00:17:17,140
Or

360
00:17:17,700 --> 00:17:18,860
is it convenient at noon?

361
00:17:18,860 --> 00:17:19,700
We can have lunch.

362
00:17:19,940 --> 00:17:21,140
Sure, I'll ask her later.

363
00:17:21,140 --> 00:17:21,980
Thanks.

364
00:17:33,940 --> 00:17:34,780
Ms. Wei.

365
00:17:35,580 --> 00:17:36,420
You're here.

366
00:17:37,940 --> 00:17:39,500
How did the talks with Yixiu go?

367
00:17:39,860 --> 00:17:40,700
Pretty smoothly.

368
00:17:40,700 --> 00:17:42,660
They're preparing the letter of intent.

369
00:17:42,980 --> 00:17:43,820
That's great.

370
00:17:44,260 --> 00:17:46,300
Many people are waiting
for the letter of intent.

371
00:17:46,300 --> 00:17:48,260
Once it arrives,
they can transfer the funds.

372
00:17:48,780 --> 00:17:49,820
So we need to hurry.

373
00:17:49,820 --> 00:17:50,660
Got it.

374
00:17:52,100 --> 00:17:52,940
By the way,

375
00:17:53,380 --> 00:17:54,620
Yiming told me

376
00:17:55,180 --> 00:17:56,980
Tang Yang has been digging up

377
00:17:56,980 --> 00:17:58,740
CBBC Bank's small loans

378
00:17:58,740 --> 00:17:59,900
from a few years back.

379
00:18:00,940 --> 00:18:02,460
I hope you can arrange

380
00:18:02,460 --> 00:18:03,300
to meet her

381
00:18:03,940 --> 00:18:04,820
and find a chance

382
00:18:04,820 --> 00:18:05,900
to tell her

383
00:18:06,540 --> 00:18:07,380
some things are

384
00:18:07,380 --> 00:18:08,780
better left undisturbed.

385
00:18:12,860 --> 00:18:13,940
Can you

386
00:18:14,660 --> 00:18:15,940
clarify this for me, Ms. Wei?

387
00:18:16,980 --> 00:18:18,340
I need to ensure that Tang Yang

388
00:18:18,900 --> 00:18:19,900
doesn't misunderstand.

389
00:18:29,740 --> 00:18:31,100
A few years ago,

390
00:18:31,500 --> 00:18:33,580
we borrowed some money from CBBC.

391
00:18:39,940 --> 00:18:41,780
Mom, Dad, I'm back.

392
00:18:42,100 --> 00:18:43,060
Tang is back.

393
00:18:43,940 --> 00:18:45,500
The food is all heated up.

394
00:18:46,020 --> 00:18:47,180
I'll get you a bowl of soup.

395
00:18:47,900 --> 00:18:48,740
You wash your hands.

396
00:18:49,180 --> 00:18:50,220
Dad isn't back yet?

397
00:18:50,900 --> 00:18:51,940
Your dad?

398
00:18:52,500 --> 00:18:53,340
He's out

399
00:18:53,620 --> 00:18:55,140
in the garden playing chess

400
00:18:55,140 --> 00:18:56,180
with someone.

401
00:18:57,060 --> 00:18:57,900
Look at you.

402
00:18:57,900 --> 00:18:59,540
It's been days since you last came home.

403
00:19:00,220 --> 00:19:02,220
We have a pilot project going on.

404
00:19:02,220 --> 00:19:04,580
I'm working overtime every day.

405
00:19:05,700 --> 00:19:06,580
Overtime, overtime.

406
00:19:06,580 --> 00:19:07,700
I know.

407
00:19:08,460 --> 00:19:09,980
Why did you come back today?

408
00:19:10,180 --> 00:19:11,740
Jiang Shiyan is on a business trip.

409
00:19:12,100 --> 00:19:13,020
What does that

410
00:19:13,020 --> 00:19:14,740
have to do with you coming back?

411
00:19:15,940 --> 00:19:16,780
Well...

412
00:19:18,140 --> 00:19:19,180
Because he treats me

413
00:19:19,180 --> 00:19:20,860
to dinner every day.

414
00:19:20,860 --> 00:19:21,740
When he's away,

415
00:19:21,740 --> 00:19:22,820
I have no dinner.

416
00:19:24,820 --> 00:19:26,180
Okay, okay.

417
00:19:27,020 --> 00:19:28,700
Are you going to work overtime

418
00:19:28,700 --> 00:19:29,780
this weekend?

419
00:19:30,460 --> 00:19:31,860
I don't think so.

420
00:19:31,860 --> 00:19:33,020
I can take two days off.

421
00:19:33,860 --> 00:19:34,700
By the way,

422
00:19:35,100 --> 00:19:37,700
this weekend is your
wedding anniversary, right?

423
00:19:37,700 --> 00:19:38,820
What's your plan?

424
00:19:38,820 --> 00:19:40,060
Should I book

425
00:19:40,060 --> 00:19:41,300
a vacation resort for us?

426
00:19:41,300 --> 00:19:42,860
We can have fun there; it's on me.

427
00:19:42,860 --> 00:19:44,740
It's not what I mean.

428
00:19:45,300 --> 00:19:46,420
I want to arrange

429
00:19:46,700 --> 00:19:47,900
a blind date for you.

430
00:19:47,900 --> 00:19:48,740
No way.

431
00:19:48,860 --> 00:19:50,820
I'm not going; I'm not going.

432
00:19:50,820 --> 00:19:52,060
You found various excuses.

433
00:19:52,060 --> 00:19:53,780
It's the New Year;
you have training soon.

434
00:19:53,780 --> 00:19:55,220
It's been a long time.

435
00:19:55,500 --> 00:19:56,340
I won't arrange

436
00:19:56,620 --> 00:19:59,060
too many this time; just a few.

437
00:19:59,060 --> 00:20:00,660
A few decent ones for you to check out.

438
00:20:00,660 --> 00:20:02,700
I really don't want to go.

439
00:20:03,140 --> 00:20:04,700
I'm super tired, Mom.

440
00:20:04,700 --> 00:20:06,140
My voice is already hoarse.

441
00:20:06,300 --> 00:20:08,460
I just want to sleep well.

442
00:20:08,820 --> 00:20:10,380
I understand it.

443
00:20:10,380 --> 00:20:12,180
You can sleep in the morning

444
00:20:12,180 --> 00:20:13,300
and go afterward.

445
00:20:13,300 --> 00:20:14,420
I won't arrange too many.

446
00:20:14,420 --> 00:20:15,260
Just a few.

447
00:20:15,260 --> 00:20:16,620
They are decent candidates.

448
00:20:16,620 --> 00:20:17,540
Just take a look then.

449
00:20:19,540 --> 00:20:20,380
I'm really not going.

450
00:20:20,700 --> 00:20:22,020
Mom, I'll go with you

451
00:20:22,020 --> 00:20:23,180
to celebrate your anniversary.

452
00:20:24,780 --> 00:20:26,220
It's been arranged

453
00:20:26,220 --> 00:20:28,220
long ago by your dad and me.

454
00:20:28,540 --> 00:20:30,300
We're going to a five-star hotel

455
00:20:30,300 --> 00:20:31,540
for a buffet

456
00:20:31,700 --> 00:20:34,060
and Qinglong Lake for some fun.

457
00:20:34,460 --> 00:20:36,820
You weren't there at our wedding,

458
00:20:37,220 --> 00:20:38,900
so our anniversary

459
00:20:38,900 --> 00:20:39,900
doesn't need you.

460
00:20:40,620 --> 00:20:42,700
Going on a blind date

461
00:20:43,180 --> 00:20:44,700
is the best gift you can give us

462
00:20:44,700 --> 00:20:45,620
for our anniversary.

463
00:20:47,420 --> 00:20:48,260
Tang?

464
00:20:53,900 --> 00:20:55,020
I'll fly to Shenzhen.

465
00:20:55,180 --> 00:20:57,180
Arrange a meeting with Mr. Chen
from Tiange.

466
00:20:57,180 --> 00:20:58,660
And one with Ding Shen Capital.

467
00:20:58,940 --> 00:21:01,420
Okay. How did the meeting
with Wannian Foods go?

468
00:21:02,140 --> 00:21:03,300
I suddenly had an idea,

469
00:21:03,580 --> 00:21:05,100
but right now, I'm still in the car.

470
00:21:05,100 --> 00:21:06,300
I'll talk to you later.

471
00:21:07,860 --> 00:21:08,700
Bye-bye.

472
00:21:12,940 --> 00:21:14,260
(Tang)
When will you be back?

473
00:21:14,780 --> 00:21:15,980
Ms. Zhou arranged a blind date

474
00:21:15,980 --> 00:21:16,980
this weekend.

475
00:21:21,340 --> 00:21:22,180
Hello?

476
00:21:23,180 --> 00:21:24,180
Why is your voice hoarse?

477
00:21:24,940 --> 00:21:27,020
I had meetings all day today.

478
00:21:27,020 --> 00:21:28,420
My voice is almost gone.

479
00:21:28,420 --> 00:21:29,420
Drink some water

480
00:21:29,420 --> 00:21:30,260
with tangerine peel.

481
00:21:32,900 --> 00:21:33,940
I won't go on a blind date.

482
00:21:34,260 --> 00:21:35,900
Of course not.

483
00:21:36,300 --> 00:21:37,180
Absolutely not, okay?

484
00:21:38,220 --> 00:21:39,700
Why don't you tell your parents

485
00:21:39,860 --> 00:21:41,020
that we're dating?

486
00:21:41,780 --> 00:21:42,660
That way, she won't

487
00:21:42,660 --> 00:21:43,500
force you to go.

488
00:21:44,420 --> 00:21:45,260
Sounds good.

489
00:21:46,700 --> 00:21:48,220
Good idea. Let's do it.

490
00:21:48,220 --> 00:21:49,180
I'll tell her right now.

491
00:21:53,020 --> 00:21:54,860
I have something to announce to you.

492
00:21:55,500 --> 00:21:57,300
What is it? You're so serious.

493
00:22:00,660 --> 00:22:01,580
I'm in a relationship.

494
00:22:02,180 --> 00:22:03,300
You're in a relationship?

495
00:22:03,460 --> 00:22:04,980
Great. Who is it?

496
00:22:04,980 --> 00:22:06,340
Is it a colleague or...

497
00:22:06,340 --> 00:22:07,380
With Jiang Shiyan.

498
00:22:19,700 --> 00:22:20,540
Tang,

499
00:22:21,820 --> 00:22:23,540
I know you don't want a blind date,

500
00:22:23,780 --> 00:22:25,140
but there's no need to lie to us.

501
00:22:25,340 --> 00:22:26,180
I...

502
00:22:26,220 --> 00:22:27,700
I'm not lying to you.

503
00:22:29,460 --> 00:22:31,060
- You and Jiang Shiyan?
- Right.

504
00:22:31,060 --> 00:22:32,740
You two are dating?

505
00:22:32,740 --> 00:22:33,580
Yes.

506
00:22:36,980 --> 00:22:37,980
I see.

507
00:22:38,740 --> 00:22:39,620
You're just like

508
00:22:39,900 --> 00:22:41,860
those people online,

509
00:22:41,860 --> 00:22:43,900
making up a fake relationship

510
00:22:43,900 --> 00:22:45,260
with a good friend

511
00:22:45,420 --> 00:22:46,420
to avoid

512
00:22:46,580 --> 00:22:48,100
family pressure

513
00:22:48,100 --> 00:22:50,220
and to save yourself
from nagging at home.

514
00:22:50,780 --> 00:22:51,980
Tang,

515
00:22:52,420 --> 00:22:54,660
I'm not urging you to get married.

516
00:22:55,180 --> 00:22:56,100
I just think

517
00:22:56,100 --> 00:22:57,460
you should date.

518
00:22:57,460 --> 00:22:58,540
It's a normal

519
00:22:58,540 --> 00:23:00,500
emotional need in life.

520
00:23:00,500 --> 00:23:01,820
You can't just work

521
00:23:01,820 --> 00:23:03,060
without a life.

522
00:23:03,660 --> 00:23:07,220
I'm not avoiding blind dates.

523
00:23:07,500 --> 00:23:09,780
I really am dating him.

524
00:23:10,060 --> 00:23:12,100
We're truly in love.

525
00:23:13,580 --> 00:23:14,540
Tang, don't forget

526
00:23:14,900 --> 00:23:16,580
I'm a teacher.

527
00:23:16,860 --> 00:23:18,660
I've been teaching for decades.

528
00:23:18,660 --> 00:23:20,220
Early relationships are common.

529
00:23:20,220 --> 00:23:21,420
I can tell right away

530
00:23:21,420 --> 00:23:22,900
whether there's a romantic thing.

531
00:23:23,380 --> 00:23:25,220
You and Jiang Shiyan?

532
00:23:25,620 --> 00:23:26,740
Do you want to fool me

533
00:23:26,740 --> 00:23:28,060
with your small tricks?

534
00:23:28,580 --> 00:23:29,580
If I can be fooled,

535
00:23:29,820 --> 00:23:31,020
I've truly wasted my years

536
00:23:31,020 --> 00:23:32,900
as a senior teacher.

537
00:23:33,060 --> 00:23:35,700
You... You...

538
00:23:37,780 --> 00:23:38,620
Forget it, forget it.

539
00:23:39,460 --> 00:23:40,300
It's fine.

540
00:23:40,820 --> 00:23:41,820
Our talk ends here.

541
00:23:43,220 --> 00:23:44,060
I'm leaving.

542
00:23:44,100 --> 00:23:45,180
Tang, where are you going?

543
00:23:45,620 --> 00:23:47,380
I'm going back. I don't want to stay.

544
00:23:47,380 --> 00:23:48,660
Then be careful

545
00:23:48,660 --> 00:23:49,500
on the way.

546
00:23:58,580 --> 00:24:00,300
Do you think my analysis is correct?

547
00:24:01,540 --> 00:24:02,740
Well,

548
00:24:03,380 --> 00:24:04,580
there's some truth to it.

549
00:24:05,620 --> 00:24:06,980
You're pretty sharp.

550
00:24:07,220 --> 00:24:08,620
I never expected that Tang

551
00:24:08,620 --> 00:24:09,900
doesn't even want to date.

552
00:24:10,260 --> 00:24:11,620
Of course.

553
00:24:12,460 --> 00:24:13,380
When I was

554
00:24:13,380 --> 00:24:14,780
a head teacher,

555
00:24:14,780 --> 00:24:15,620
I could tell

556
00:24:16,060 --> 00:24:17,060
when a student lied

557
00:24:17,060 --> 00:24:18,380
with one look.

558
00:24:19,860 --> 00:24:21,460
Are you sure you didn't wrong Tang?

559
00:24:23,140 --> 00:24:23,980
I wronged her?

560
00:24:24,140 --> 00:24:25,220
What do you mean?

561
00:24:25,460 --> 00:24:26,940
Do you think they might

562
00:24:27,380 --> 00:24:28,820
really be dating?

563
00:24:38,660 --> 00:24:40,980
Cut to the chase; what's going on?

564
00:24:42,020 --> 00:24:43,220
How could that be?

565
00:24:43,940 --> 00:24:45,100
I knew it.

566
00:24:46,220 --> 00:24:47,300
I think

567
00:24:47,540 --> 00:24:48,460
maybe this idea

568
00:24:48,460 --> 00:24:50,740
is Jiang Shiyan's.

569
00:24:51,420 --> 00:24:52,780
No way.

570
00:24:53,740 --> 00:24:55,540
I know my son too well.

571
00:24:56,140 --> 00:24:57,900
He often can't come up with anything,

572
00:24:57,900 --> 00:24:59,740
but when it comes to sneaky stuff

573
00:24:59,740 --> 00:25:00,980
or tricks,

574
00:25:00,980 --> 00:25:01,820
he's always spot on.

575
00:25:02,540 --> 00:25:04,180
Look, it must be like this:

576
00:25:04,540 --> 00:25:05,980
Tang tells Jiang Shiyan

577
00:25:05,980 --> 00:25:07,580
that you want her to go on a blind date.

578
00:25:07,580 --> 00:25:08,500
She doesn't want to go.

